{"id":609136,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/【立此存照】巴黎圣母院着火之后-战狼式狂欢/","date":"2019-04-16T08:26:18Z","modified":"2019-04-16T08:26:18Z","title":"【立此存照】巴黎圣母院着火之后 “战狼式狂欢”热评前四","content":"<p>4月15日，法国巴黎著名标志性古建筑巴黎圣母院被一场大火吞噬，目前火势已被扑灭，建筑的尖塔及屋顶部分遭到焚毁，损失巨大，目前起火原因暂不明确。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Mourning crowd sings &#39;Ave Maria&#39; outside Notre Dame cathedral amid devastating fire. <a href=\"https://t.co/4UosoXj1K1\">https://t.co/4UosoXj1K1</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/NNi308gqE7\">pic.twitter.com/NNi308gqE7</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; ABC News (@ABC) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ABC/status/1118052973370925056?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 16, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>该事件发生后，有不少中国网民对此表示“幸灾乐祸”，以“火烧圆明园”进行对比。中共官媒甚至刊文<a href=\"https://news.163.com/19/0416/11/ECSP3AJD0001875P.html\">《央视网评:国耻不能忘却 但不应该落井下石》</a>呼吁保持理智&#8221;不应该打着历史的名义发泄自己的情绪&#8221;。</p>\n<p>截至4月16日北京时间16点，北美留学生日报相关文章<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mk7zo4cMNfMjDcC-X9ZlxQ\">《突发！巴黎圣母院大火！800年古迹被焚毁，全人类最伤心的一天…》</a>热门评论前四截图如下：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-609137\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"734\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0243.jpg 1124w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0243-204x300.jpg 204w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0243-768x1127.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0243-698x1024.jpg 698w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-609138\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0244.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0244.jpg 1125w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0244-211x300.jpg 211w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0244-768x1094.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/IMG_0244-719x1024.jpg 719w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1019,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[38376,33704]}